headline: Ecolab Life Sciences Opens New State-of-the-Art Bioprocessing Applications Laboratory in Pennsylvania, US
summary: ST. PAUL, Minn., May 14, 2025--Ecolab announces the opening of its new US Bioprocessing Applications Laboratory based in King of Prussia, PA.
